Module es.uvigo.esei.sing.textproc.step.corenlpentityextraction

Package es.uvigo.esei.sing.textproc.step.corenlpentityextraction

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CoreNLPEntityExtractionProcessingStep
    Extracts new named entities from the input documents, from a seed set of named entities, using the bootstrapped pattern-based learning algorithm included with CoreNLP.
    CoreNLPEntityExtractionProcessingStepService
    The service implementation for this processing step.
    NamedEntityDictionaryHelper
    Contains helper methods for dealing with the contents of preexisting, internal use named entity dictionaries.
    NamedEntityDictionaryHelper.NamedEntityTerm
    Represents a named entity term, which can have synonyms.
    NamedEntityDictionaryHelper.PropertyWithTemporaryFiles
    Holds the value for a property, and also provides a NamedEntityDictionaryHelper.PropertyWithTemporaryFiles.close() method to release temporary files created for this property.
    NERMappingsFileWriter
    Writes NER mappings to a file, in the format specified by TokensRegexNERAnnotator.
